53
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,200
 to the will of God.

54
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:13,460
 He quoted one of his favorite Bible verses, Isaiah 6, verse 8.

55
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:16,660
 Here I am, Lord.

56
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:19,780
 Send me.

57
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:25,440
 After Charlie finished, I met him backstage

58
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:28,920
 and I spoke to him and I'll never forget this.

59
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,560
 I said, Charlie baby,

60
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:35,300
 please talk to me next time before you say that statement.

61
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:40,280
 Because when you say something like that,

62
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:44,540
 there is so much power in that verse.

63
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:49,820
 When you say, here I am, Lord, use me.

64
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:55,260
 God will take you up on that.

65
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:58,860
 And he did with Charlie.

66
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:14,120
 Eleven days ago,

67
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:18,380
 God accepted that total surrender from my husband

68
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:21,560
 and then called him to his side.

69
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:26,080
 More than anything, Charlie wanted to do,

70
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:28,000
 not his will, but God's will.

71
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,560
 And over these past eleven days,

72
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:34,560
 through all the pain,

73
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:39,240
 never before have I found as much comfort

74
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,700
 as I now do

75
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:44,280
 in the words of our Lord's Prayer,

76
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,720
 thy will be done.

77
00:03:46,720 --> 00:04:03,580
 God's love was revealed to me on the very day

78
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:05,280
 my husband was murdered.

79
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:09,500
 On the afternoon of September 10th,

80
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,240
 I arrived at a Utah hospital

81
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,160
 to do the unthinkable,

82
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:16,200
 to look directly

83
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:19,320
 at my husband's murdered body.

84
00:04:19,320 --> 00:04:24,340
 I saw the wound that ended his life.

85
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:29,480
 I felt everything you would expect to feel.

86
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:32,400
 I felt shock.

87
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:32,460
 I felt shock.

88
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:35,060
 I felt horror.

89
00:04:35,060 --> 00:04:39,400
 And a level of heartache

90
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:43,140
 that I didn't even know existed.

91
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:48,520
 But there was something else too.

92
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:52,040
 even in death,

93
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,420
 I could see the man that I love.

94
00:04:54,420 --> 00:05:02,360
 I saw the one single gray hair

95
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,960
 on the side of his head,

96
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,760
 which I never told him about.

97
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,800
 Now he knows.

98
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,200
 Sorry, baby.

99
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:10,920
 I'm telling you now,

100
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,400
 but never told him.

101
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,680
 Didn't want to.

102
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,380
 I also saw this.

103
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:22,180
 I also saw on his lips

104
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:24,880
 the faintest smile.

105
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:29,180
 And that told me something important.

106
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:33,460
 It revealed to me

107
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:35,400
 a great mercy from God

108
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:36,360
 in this tragedy.

109
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:39,860
 When I saw that,

110
00:05:39,860 --> 00:05:41,040
 it told me

111
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,220
 that Charlie didn't suffer.

112
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:46,580
 Even the doctor told me.

113
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:49,660
 it was something so instant

114
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:50,360
 that even

115
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,880
 even if Charlie had been shot

116
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,360
 in the operating room itself,

117
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:57,460
 nothing could have been done.

118
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:00,240
 There was no pain.

119
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:02,420
 There was no fear.

120
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,620
 No agony.

121
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:05,320
 One moment,

122
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,000
 Charlie was doing what he loved.

123
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,520
 Arguing and debating on campus.

124
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:13,940
 Fighting for the gospel.

125
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:16,540
 in truth.

126
00:06:16,540 --> 00:06:19,680
 In front of a big crowd.

127
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,460
 And then he blinked.

128
00:06:22,460 --> 00:06:24,960
 He blinked.

129
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:28,560
 And saw his Savior in paradise.

130
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:43,900
 And all the heavenly mysteries

131
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:45,000
 were revealed to him.

132
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:49,220
 God's love

133
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:52,160
 continued to be revealed to me

134
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,200
 in the days that followed.

135
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:57,240
 But most of all,

136
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,800
 God's mercy and God's love

137
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,200
 have been revealed to me

138
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,340
 these past 10 days.

139
00:07:01,340 --> 00:07:04,720
 After Charlie's assassination,

140
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,720
 we didn't see violence.

141
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,440
 We didn't see rioting.

142
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:10,500
 We didn't see rioting.

143
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:24,060
 We didn't see revolution.

144
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,900
 We didn't see revolution.

145
00:07:25,900 --> 00:07:29,660
 Instead, we saw what my husband

146
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,880
 always prayed he would see

147
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,700
 in this country.

148
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:34,280
 We saw revival.

149
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:49,600
 This past week,

150
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,200
 we saw people open a Bible

151
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,160
 for the first time

152
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:52,700
 in a decade.

153
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:56,300
 We saw people pray for the first time

154
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,220
 since they were children.

155
00:07:57,220 --> 00:08:00,820
 We saw people go to a church service

156
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:01,740
 for the first time

157
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:02,940
 in their entire lives.

158
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:16,020
 Charlie liked to journal.

159
00:08:16,020 --> 00:08:18,860
 And I say this because

160
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:20,780
 he did it to remember

161
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:22,360
 important moments and sayings

162
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,200
 that affected him.

163
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:26,100
 And one of the things

164
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:27,220
 he wrote in his journal

165
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:28,600
 was this.

166
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:34,860
 Every time you make a decision,

167
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:38,420
 it puts a mark on your soul.

168
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:44,140
 To those of you out there

169
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,600
 who just made that decision

170
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:49,440
 and took the first step

171
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,700
 toward a spiritual life,

172
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:54,380
 I say thank you and welcome.

173
00:08:54,380 --> 00:09:06,140
 One day, I hope you look back

174
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:08,320
 and realize it was the most important

175
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,520
 decision of your life

176
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,140
 because it is.

177
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:14,480
 All of you,

178
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:19,480
 all of you who are already believers,

179
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,900
 it is your job

180
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:22,240
 to shepherd these people.

181
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:25,160
 Do not take that lightly.

182
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:29,100
 Water the seed of their faith.

183
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:32,880
 Protect it and help it grow.

184
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:37,960
 Every day as Charlie

185
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,680
 rode into the office,

186
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:42,140
 he would go through

187
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:43,320
 his contact list

188
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,440
 and I know there's

189
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,340
 many of you

190
00:09:45,340 --> 00:09:47,360
 who were impacted by this.

191
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,320
 He would go through

192
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,340
 his contact list

193
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:50,660
 and send Bible verses

194
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:51,620
 for the day.

195
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:54,220
 He knew that faith

196
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:54,920
 was a habit.

197
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:57,640
 The more you live it,

198
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,600
 the more it grows.

199
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:02,020
 But know this too.

200
00:10:02,020 --> 00:10:05,580
 The seed has only

201
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:06,480
 just been planted.

202
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,420
 The enemy will tempt you

203
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:12,320
 the most

204
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,640
 in a time like this one.

205
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:16,560
 God will always be there

206
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:16,940
 for you,

207
00:10:16,940 --> 00:10:18,260
 but you must choose

208
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:20,160
 to mark your soul

209
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,820
 again

210
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:23,300
 and again

211
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:24,520
 in the direction

212
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,580
 of Christ.

213
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:35,700
 Pray again.

214
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:38,040
 Read the Bible again.

215
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:40,680
 Go to church next Sunday

216
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:42,800
 and the Sunday after that

217
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,160
 and break free

218
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,240
 from the temptations

219
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,020
 and shackles

220
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:46,880
 of this world.

221
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:58,100
 Being a follower

222
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:58,700
 of Christ

223
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,620
 is not easy.

224
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:02,240
 It's not supposed to be.

225
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:04,940
 Jesus said,

226
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:05,480
 if anyone

227
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,040
 would come after me,

228
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:08,500
 let him deny himself,

229
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:09,920
 take up his cross

230
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:10,800
 and follow me.

231
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,600
 He said he would

232
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,380
 be persecuted.

233
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:16,360
 He said we would

234
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,140
 be persecuted

235
00:11:17,140 --> 00:11:18,160
 and Charlie knew

236
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,580
 that and happily

237
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,660
 carried his cross

238
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:21,440
 all the way

239
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,000
 to the end.

240
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:26,240
 And I want all

241
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:26,980
 of you to know

242
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:30,560
 while Charlie died

243
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,720
 far too early,

244
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,700
 he was also

245
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:34,720
 ready to die.

246
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,720
 There was nothing,

247
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,460
 nothing he was

248
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:40,100
 putting off.

249
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:41,600
 There was nothing

250
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,500
 that was too hard

251
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,420
 or too painful

252
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:45,100
 or nothing

253
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:46,140
 that he just felt

254
00:11:46,140 --> 00:11:47,040
 like he didn't

255
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,120
 want to do it.

256
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:50,560
 He left this world

257
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:51,500
 without regrets.

258
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:55,260
 He did 100%

259
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:55,860
 of what he could

260
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:56,360
 every day.

261
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:59,180
 But I want you

262
00:11:59,180 --> 00:11:59,980
 to know something.

263
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:03,660
 Charlie died

264
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:05,380
 with incomplete work

265
00:12:05,380 --> 00:12:07,900
 but not with

266
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,140
 unfinished business.

267
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:21,820
 But I will miss him.

268
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:27,440
 I will miss him

269
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,180
 so much

270
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,480
 because our marriage

271
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,580
 and our family

272
00:12:30,580 --> 00:12:31,580
 were beautiful.

273
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:33,080
 They still are.

274
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:42,760
 The greatest cause

275
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:43,620
 in Charlie's life

276
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:44,820
 was trying to revive

277
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:46,080
 the American family.

278
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,420
 When he spoke

279
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:49,160
 to young people,

280
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,460
 he was always eager

281
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:51,160
 to tell them

282
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,280
 about God's vision

283
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,500
 for marriage

284
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:55,320
 and how

285
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,620
 if they could just

286
00:12:56,620 --> 00:12:57,780
 dare to live it out,

287
00:12:57,780 --> 00:13:00,180
 it would enrich

288
00:13:00,180 --> 00:13:01,020
 every part

289
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:01,700
 of their life

290
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:02,580
 in the same way

291
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,420
 that it enriched

292
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:03,980
